member.summary:
Wrap an  with the SpendGuard middleware. Use
inside an IChatClientBuilder pipeline:

services.AddChatClient(...).Use((inner, sp) => inner.UseSpendGuard(sp));

member.param:
Optional dummy address. gRPC.NET needs a non-empty URI even on UDS;
the default http://localhost is overridden by the connect
callback. Override only when stitching multiple sidecars in a test.

member.summary:
Run-level projection columns (3 per spec §2.2).
NUMERIC(38,0) serialized as int64 here (assumes < 2^63 atomic units;
for larger budgets a future v2 may switch to string per Money type).
